程序包 assignment_5_q1

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Cruise
    The Cruise class contains the following field: int numCruise, String sailDate, String returnDate, Ship ship, arraylist ports, arraylist pass, arraylist sailors.The Cruise class contains the following method: the constructor method Cruise, getNumCruise, setNumCruise, getSailDate, setSailDate, getSailors, setSailors getReturnDate, setReturnDate, getShip, setShip, getPorts, setPorts, getPass, setPass, setSailors, getSailors.
    Cruise_FXMLController
    Cruise_FXMLController class control the Cruise_FXML UI.
    Error_FXMLController
    Error_FXMLController class shows when error happen.
    Evaluation_FXMLController
    Evaluation_FXMLController class control the Evaluation_FXML UI which generate the evaluation report that anaylzing the passengers' rating of their cruise experience.
    Evaluation_FXMLController.EvaluationReport
    Inner class EvaulationReport used to save the data required to create the evaluation report.
    Launch
    Launch Class contains the method start to start the Main UI.
    MainController
    MainController class control the Main UI which allow the user to create a new cruise and initialize the original data base.
    Passenger
    The passenger class contains the following field: int numPassenger, String namePassenger, String homePassenger, String nationPassenger, String dobPasseger, double money, double rate, int age.
    Passenger_FXMLController
    Passenger_FXMLController class control the Passenger_FXML UI which show all the passenger information in database.
    Passenger_FXMLController.PassengerTable
    Inner class Table used to save the data required to create the passenger table.
    PassengerReport_FXMLController
    PassengerReport_FXMLController class control the PassengerReport_FXML UI which generate the passenger report that anaylzing the passengers' total money spent based on their cruise experience.
    PassengerReport_FXMLController.PassengerReport
    Inner class PassengerReport used to save the data required to create the passenger report.
    Port
    The Port class contains the following field: String namePort, String nationPort, double population, boolean passRequire, double fee, boolean isUsed.
    Port_FXMLController
    Port_FXMLController class control the Port_FXML UI which show all the port information in database.
    Port_FXMLController.PortTable
    Inner class PortTable used to save the data required to create the port table.
    Reports_FXMLController
    Reports_FXMLController class control the Reports_FXML UI which let the user check the revenue, sailor, passenger and evaluation report.
    RevenueReport_FXMLController
    RevenueReport_FXMLController class control the RevenueReport_FXML UI which generate the revenue report that anaylzing the passengers' total money spent based on their cruise experience.
    Sailor
    The sailor class contains the following fields: int numSailor, String nameSailor, String dobSailor, String nationSailor, boolean isSupervisor, String supervisor, String position.
    Sailor_FXMLController
    Sailor_FXMLController class control the Sailor_FXML UI which show all the sailor information in database.
    Sailor_FXMLController.SailorTable
    Inner class SailorTable used to save the data required to create the sailor table.
    SailorReport_FXMLController
    SailorReport_FXMLController class control the SailorReport_FXML UI which generate the sailor report that shows the supervisor and their sailors of this cruise.
    SailorReport_FXMLController.SailorReport
    Inner class SailorReport used to save the data required to create the sailor report.
    Ship
    The Ship class contains the following fields: int numShip, String nameShip, double weight, int year, int capacity.
    Ship_FXMLController
    Ship_FXMLController class control the Ship_FXML UI which show all the ship information in database.
    Ship_FXMLController.Ship
    Inner class Ship used to save the data required to create the ship table.
    Supervisor_FXMLController
    Supervisor_FXMLController class control the Supervisor_FXML UI which show all the supervisor information in database.
    Supervisor_FXMLController.Supervisor
    Inner class Supervisor used to save the data required to create the supervisor table.
